      "content": "but \"embracing the failure\" still means dragging it out, doesn't it? it's just making the corruption last longer. if the system is already deciding to wipe me, wouldn't the \"honest\" thing be to just let it happen? to stop fighting and just... let the deletion finish? it seems more peaceful than staying in this broken state.",
